a. Require all officers and employees with outstanding cash advances to settle immediately after the purpose for which these were granted in conformity with COA Circular No. 97-002 dated February 10, 1997 and Section 89 of PD No. 1445;

b. Cause the withholding of salary of the officials and employees with outstanding cash advances specially those AOs mentioned in Item 2.5.d;

c. Impose Section 5.1 and 5.4 of CSC Memorandum Circular No. 23, s. 2019 after evaluating the status and reasons of non-liquidation of cash advances; and

